    接口 说明
    OnPlayerAVExtraInfoListener  
    OnPlayerCachePositionUpdateListener
    Interface definition of a callback to be invoked indicating caching status of a media resource being streamed over the network.
    OnPlayerErrorListener
    Interface definition of a callback to be invoked when there has been an error during an asynchronous operation (other errors will throw exceptions at method call time).
    OnPlayerFirstVideoFrameShowListener
    Interface definition of a callback to be invoked when the first video frame has been rendered, then you can remove the Cover.
    OnPlayerInfoListener
    Interface definition of a callback to be invoked when some info about with media file or player is update.
    OnPlayerLoadingUpdateListener
    Interface definition of callback to be invoked when the loading update.
    OnPlayerNetRequestStatusListener  
    OnPlayerPlayCompletionListener
    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when playback of a media source has completed.
    OnPlayerPlayPositionUpdateListener
    Interface definition of a callback to be invoked when the play position update, and then you can Update UI.
    OnPlayerQualityMonitorListener  
    OnPlayerStateUpdateListener
    Interface definition of a callback when the player engine state update.
    OnPlayerStatisticsListener
    Interface definition of callback to be invoked when a playing task is finished(stopped) and return some statistics associate with the playing task.
